snippet.textDisplay:
Wow !! first thanks to Ram Sampath for introducing us to some great fusion. Slowly I have started feeling that your music is addictive and slow medicine like AR Rahman. The more I listen to your music the more addictive it is. Rappers were really cool, good to see some rap other than English and Punjabi, and foremost sensible rap, not the party/girls rap. And kudos to Vidya Harikrishna, you are unshakable. I saw couple of other songs that you have sung and the general setup for Carnatic music is Violins and Mridungam, to get out of that environment and sing in this setup live. Hatsoff mam
And Ram again thanks to you for introducing us the excellent vocalists like Vidya Harikrishna and Bhanvari Devi
snippet.textOriginal:
Wow !! first thanks to Ram Sampath for introducing us to some great fusion. Slowly I have started feeling that your music is addictive and slow medicine like AR Rahman. The more I listen to your music the more addictive it is. Rappers were really cool, good to see some rap other than English and Punjabi, and foremost sensible rap, not the party/girls rap. And kudos to Vidya Harikrishna, you are unshakable. I saw couple of other songs that you have sung and the general setup for Carnatic music is Violins and Mridungam, to get out of that environment and sing in this setup live. Hatsoff mam
